                            <comment id="44735" author="mdiep" created="Wed, 12 Sep 2012 23:17:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch for master &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3963&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3963&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="44670" author="liwei" created="Wed, 12 Sep 2012 03:42:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;On master and 2.3, the file system type check must base on facet_fstype() rather than directly on the environment variables.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
